CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 6, 1952, page 13, reads: "Presiding - Sheriff Thomas E. Whitten, GOP County Chairman, and Mrs. Nellie Dressler, shown above, were in charge of the Republican Victory Banquet held Saturday Night in the Syria Mosque Dinning Room Fred Obley was chairman of arrangements."
TitMainTitle: GOP County Chairman, Sheriff Thomas E. Whitten, and Nellie Dressler, standing behind banquet table with floral arrangement with letters "GOP" in the Syria Mosque dining room for the Republican Victory Banquet
